---
// src/components/whitepaper/Abstract.astro
---

<section id="abstract" class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900/10 to-gray-900/30">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">
        <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 to-purple-400">
          Abstract
        </span>
      </h2>
      
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The promise of decentralized technology—a world of open, equitable, and user-controlled digital interaction—remains a powerful driving force. However, the path to this vision has encountered significant obstacles:
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700/50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300"><strong class="text-indigo-300">Scalability Walls:</strong> Transaction performance is often insufficient for mass adoption, leading to congestion and high fees.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300"><strong class="text-indigo-300">User Experience Hurdles:</strong> Interacting with decentralized systems remains complex and requires technical knowledge.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300"><strong class="text-indigo-300">Economic Instability:</strong> It's challenging to balance tokenomic models to ensure security, genuine participation, and resistance to volatility.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300"><strong class="text-indigo-300">Re-centralization:</strong> Dependence on centralized providers or concentration of power in small groups.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300"><strong class="text-indigo-300">Limited Digital Sovereignty:</strong> Offline capabilities and true user autonomy remain constrained.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Fractal Network is designed from the ground up to address these fundamental challenges. We introduce a <strong class="text-indigo-300">sovereign Layer 0</strong> blockchain platform, built on a <strong class="text-indigo-300">two-layer DAG architecture</strong> and an innovative <strong class="text-indigo-300">intent-based execution model</strong>.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          This whitepaper details the design principles of Fractal Network, including its unique approach to empowering users through <strong class="text-indigo-300">Agent-managed micro-ledgers</strong> with offline capabilities, and a robust <strong class="text-indigo-300">Custodian Layer</strong> that ensures consensus, data availability, and verifiable integrity through <strong class="text-indigo-300">Zero-Knowledge Proofs (ZKPs)</strong>.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-indigo-900/20 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">In This Document</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300">Two-layer architecture (Agents and Custodians)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300">Intent-based execution model</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300">Dual-token economy ($FRAC and $SOLV)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300">Decentralized governance</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-300">Implementation roadmap</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
